  "Factory Genesis HFM and CIDs PAIRING": {
   "width": 11580,
   "height": 11100,
   "color": "rgb(0,0,255)",
   "labels": [
    {
     "text": "FACTORY IN LINE : GENESIS HFM and Customer IDs pairing  ",
     "color": "rgb(201,238,252)",
     "alignment": "2",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(64,0,64)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 0,
      "top": 15,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 11520
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "1) Make sure HFM is blank+ CID is virgin and verify ignition is OFF, then press the button \"ENTER GENESIS MODE\"",
     "color": "rgb(201,238,252)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 3240,
      "height": 1200,
      "width": 11280
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "2) If the GENESIS MODE is launched, then present a blank customer ID near central antenna ",
     "color": "rgb(201,238,252)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 3960,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 11280
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "CID / HFM information",
     "color": "rgb(201,238,252)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 4800,
