      "top": 480,
      "height": 7800,
      "width": 15000
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "2) Check that the BLM is blank while raising IGNITION ON and read the BLM information \" xxx_IS_BLANK\"",
     "color": "rgb(207,207,207)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 360,
      "top": 1320,
      "height": 285,
      "width": 10680
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "3) Make sure Gateway is unlocked and Ignition is Off and press the button \"Request Server BLM pairing\"",
     "color": "rgb(207,207,207)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 360,
      "top": 2040,
      "height": 300,
      "width": 8790
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "4) Select the \"Input_Data_to_server\" (19 bytes= $6717 + 17 bytes) and copy it in the application \"Pairing using DDT2000\".  ",
     "color": "rgb(207,207,207)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 360,
      "top": 3000,
      "height": 255,
      "width": 8775
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "5) Complete the frames in the application and press the button \"Calcul\". Get the \"Server answer\" (16 bytes) and copy it in SERVER_ANSWER. Then press the button \"Transmit Server Answer\" ",
     "color": "rgb(207,207,207)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 360,
      "top": 3960,
      "height": 615,
      "width": 12240
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "1) !! Check that you have access rights to the application \"Pairing using DDT2000\" on https://gco.intra.renault.fr:14053/gco/ctrl/login",
     "color": "rgb(207,207,207)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 360,
      "top": 840,
      "height": 300,
      "width": 11640
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "6) If the HFM is SA unlocked for BLM pairing then keep the Ignition Power Supply OFF,  press the button \"Authorize BLM pairing\" ",
     "color": "rgb(207,207,207)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 360,
      "top": 5520,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 12600
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "7) If the authorization to pair is TRUE, then switch Ignition Power Supply ON. If the BLM is paired, procedure exit is automatic.",
     "color": "rgb(207,207,207)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 360,
      "top": 7200,
      "height": 405,
      "width": 12240
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "BLM/ HFM INFORMATION",
     "color": "rgb(0,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 7080,
      "top": 8400,
      "height": 3360,
      "width": 8040
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MS Sans Serif",
      "size": 8.25,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "Security Access FAILURE",
     "color": "rgb(0,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 8400,
      "height": 3360,
      "width": 6840
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MS Sans Serif",
      "size": 8.25,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "8) (optional) To postpone the authorization to pair the BLM, press the button",
     "color": "rgb(207,207,207)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 360,
      "top": 7680,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 7680
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "SA Unlocked for BLM",
     "color": "rgb(207,207,207)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 840,
      "top": 5040,
      "height": 315,
      "width": 3495
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "Authorization to pair BLM",
     "color": "rgb(207,207,207)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 600,
      "top": 6720,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 3495
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
