  "APV Secure Pairing : HFM or CID": {
   "width": 15420,
   "height": 12180,
   "color": "rgb(0,0,255)",
   "labels": [
    {
     "text": "SECURED PAIRING AFTER SALES / REWORK : HFM or Customer ID pairing  ",
     "color": "rgb(128,255,128)",
     "alignment": "2",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(64,0,64)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 0,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 15120
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "PROCEDURE",
     "color": "rgb(128,255,128)",
     "alignment": "2",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(255,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 2280,
      "height": 1605,
      "width": 15120
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "1) Insert the \"After Sales code\" (16 bytes) and press \"AFTER SALES MODE\"",
     "color": "rgb(128,255,128)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 2760,
      "height": 480,
      "width": 13080
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 9.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "2) If the AFTER SALES REWORK MODE for HFM pairing is launched, then approach a CID of the vehicle to the Kazashi antenna",
     "color": "rgb(128,255,128)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 4440,
      "height": 600,
      "width": 7440
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 9.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "7) Once all the customer IDs are paired, insert in the box bellow Exit Parameter \"01\" and press the button \"EXIT AFTER SALES MODE\"",
     "color": "rgb(128,255,128)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 7680,
      "top": 7080,
      "height": 960,
      "width": 7560
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 9.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "CID / HFM INFORMATION",
     "color": "rgb(255,128,0)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 7680,
      "top": 8160,
      "height": 2640,
      "width": 7560
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MS Sans Serif",
      "size": 8.25,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "Select \"StartRoutine\" and press the button \"CID ANALYSE\"",
     "color": "rgb(255,128,0)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(15,15,15)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 480,
      "height": 1680,
      "width": 7440
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 9.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "PAIRING INFORMATION",
     "color": "rgb(255,128,0)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 8160,
      "height": 840,
      "width": 7440
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MS Sans Serif",
      "size": 8.25,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "STATUS MODE FAILURES",
     "color": "rgb(255,128,0)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 9120,
      "height": 2760,
      "width": 7440
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MS Sans Serif",
      "size": 8.25,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "6) Select\"StartRoutine\" and press \"CID Pairing\" to pair a customer ID",
     "color": "rgb(128,255,128)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 7680,
      "top": 5160,
      "height": 1800,
      "width": 7560
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 9.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "5) Enter AFTER SALES REWORK MODE again to launch the customer ID pairing, then approach a CID of the vehicle, or blank CID, to the Kazashi antenna",
     "color": "rgb(128,255,128)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 7680,
      "top": 4440,
      "height": 600,
      "width": 7560
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 9.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "3) Select \"StartRoutine\" and press \"HFM pairing\" to pair the HFM",
     "color": "rgb(128,255,128)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 5160,
      "height": 1800,
      "width": 7440
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 9.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "4) If the HFM is paired, the EXIT of the AFTER SALES MODE is automatic. To pair all the customer IDs follow the procedure from steps 5 to 7",
     "color": "rgb(128,255,128)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 7080,
      "height": 960,
      "width": 7440
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 9.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "After Sales Code",
     "color": "rgb(128,255,128)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 360,
      "top": 3360,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 1815
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 11.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
