  "APV Secure Pairing : Powertrain": {
   "width": 15300,
   "height": 9540,
   "color": "rgb(128,0,0)",
   "labels": [
    {
     "text": "ENGINE CONTROL MODULE: SECURED PAIRING",
     "color": "rgb(128,255,0)",
     "alignment": "2",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(15,15,15)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 0,
      "height": 300,
      "width": 15000
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "PROCEDURE",
     "color": "rgb(128,255,0)",
     "alignment": "2",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(255,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 600,
      "height": 5520,
      "width": 15000
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "1)                 Check that the ECM is blank, raise IGNITION ON and read the ECM information \" ECM_IS_BLANK\"",
     "color": "rgb(128,255,0)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 360,
      "top": 1080,
      "height": 285,
      "width": 10680
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "3) Insert the CAPV code and press the button \"AUTHORIZE ECM PAIRING IN AFTER SALES\"",
     "color": "rgb(128,255,0)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 360,
      "top": 2640,
      "height": 300,
      "width": 8790
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "4) If the authorization to pair is TRUE, then raise IGNITION ON. If the ECM is paired, procedure exit is automatic.",
     "color": "rgb(128,255,0)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 360,
      "top": 3840,
      "height": 405,
      "width": 12240
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "ECM / HFM INFORMATION",
     "color": "rgb(0,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 7080,
